									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch5.p1",
									"fallback": "The archives of Helheim are vaster than I imagined. Each new Hel seems to have contributed to this collection of knowledge."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch5.p2",
									"fallback": "I couldn't have dreamed better, I am the eleventh incarnation of Hel."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch5.p3",
									"fallback": "I found a particularly touching account from Hel II. She warns against using the power of immortality - an irreversible gift that persists even after our \"games\" end."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch5.p4",
									"fallback": "Yet, she too succumbed to this temptation. She speaks of a wise old man to whom she offered eternity, seduced by his knowledge."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch5.p5",
									"fallback": "Their love story runs through the pages of her journals."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch5.p6",
									"fallback": "So two immortals walk somewhere in this world... Bearing the burden of our \"game\" for eternity."
								}
